tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT FUNNEL(${journey.where-1} AS "${journey.header-1}",${journey.where-2} AS "${journey.header-2}",${journey.where-3} AS "${journey.header-3}",${journey.where-4} AS "${journey.header-4}",${journey.where-5} AS "${journey.header-5}",${journey.where-6} AS "${journey.header-6}",${journey.where-7} AS "${journey.header-7}",${journey.where-8} AS "${journey.header-8}",${journey.where-9} AS "${journey.header-9}",${journey.where-last} ${conversionMessage} AS "${journey.header-last}") FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause} ${uspClause}

tiles.name: Step1Abandons
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Abandons" from usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause} ${uspClause} and ${journey.where-1} and not ${journey.where-2}

tiles.name: Step5Abandons

tiles.name: Step6Abandons
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Abandons" from usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause} ${uspClause} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and not ${journey.where-7}

tiles.name: Step9Abandons
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Abandons" from usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause} ${uspClause} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9}and not ${journey.where-last}

tiles.name: StepLastAbandons
tiles.query: select 0 as "Abandons" from usersession limit 1

tiles.name: StepsQuery
tiles.query:
SELECT distinct datetime(endtime,"M-d HH:mm","10m"), 
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1}) AS "${journey.header-1}", 
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2}) AS "${journey.header-2}", 
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3}) AS "${journey.header-3}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4}) AS "${journey.header-4}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5}) AS "${journey.header-5}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6}) AS "${journey.header-6}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7}) AS "${journey.header-7}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8}) AS "${journey.header-8}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9}) AS "${journey.header-9}", CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9} and ${journey.where-last}) AS "${journey.header-last}" 
from usersession

tiles.name: Apdex2Query
tiles.query:
SELECT distinct datetime(endtime,"M-d HH:mm","10m"),
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userexperiencescore="SATISFIED") as "Satisfied",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userexperiencescore="TOLERATED") as "Tolerated",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userexperiencescore="FRUSTRATED") as "Frustrated",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9} and ${journey.where-last}) AS "Conversions" 
FROM usersession 
WHERE userActionCount>2

tiles.name: EngageQuery
tiles.query:
SELECT distinct datetime(endtime,"M-d HH:mm","10m"),
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userActionCount>3 and duration<${durationLimit}) as "Engaged",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userActionCount< ${actionLimit} and duration>${durationLimit}) as "Non Engaged",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and userActionCount<5 and duration>${durationLimit}) as "Very Non Engaged",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9} and ${journey.where-last}) AS "Conversions" 
FROM usersession 
WHERE userActionCount>2

tiles.name: DurationQuery
tiles.query:
SELECT distinct datetime(endtime,"M-d HH:mm","10m"),
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and duration<30000) as Fast, 
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and duration BETWEEN 30000 and 60000) as Medium,
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and duration between 60000 and 300000) as Slow,
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and duration>${SessionDurationLimit}) as "Very Slow",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9} and ${journey.where-last}) AS "Conversions" 
FROM usersession
WHERE userActionCount>2

tiles.name: ErrorsQuery
tiles.query:
SELECT distinct datetime(endtime,"M-d HH:mm","10m"),
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and totalErrorCount=0) as "No Errors", 
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and totalErrorCount BETWEEN 1 and 5) as "Low Errors",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and totalErrorCount > ${SessionErrorLimit}) as "High Errors",
CONDITION(count(*), WHERE ${milestoneGoal} and ${journey.where-1} and ${journey.where-2} and ${journey.where-3} and ${journey.where-4} and ${journey.where-5} and ${journey.where-6} and ${journey.where-7} and ${journey.where-8} and ${journey.where-9} and ${journey.where-last}) AS "Conversions" 
FROM usersession
WHERE userActionCount>2

tiles.name: ConversionsThresholdQuery
tiles.query: select count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and  (${conversionGoal})

tiles.name: AbandonsThresholdQuery
tiles.query: select count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and not  (${conversionGoal})

tiles.name: SessionsThresholdQuery
tiles.query: select count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal})

tiles.name: ErrorsThresholdQuery
tiles.query: SELECT count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and (totalErrorCount > ${SessionErrorLimit} )

tiles.name: DurationThresholdQuery
tiles.query: SELECT count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and (duration>${SessionDurationLimit} )

tiles.name: ApdexThresholdQuery
tiles.query: select count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and (userexperiencescore!="SATISFIED")

tiles.name: EngageThresholdQuery
tiles.query: SELECT count(distinct userSessionId) as " " FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") and (${milestoneGoal}) and (userActionCount > 2 and userActionCount < ${actionLimit} and duration>${durationLimit} )
